      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Random Number Scheduler\n\nNo credentials required for this workflow.\n\n### How It Works\n1. Triggers every 60 seconds\n2. Generates a random number (0-999)\n3. If **even**: executes the \"Time API Logger\" workflow\n4. If **odd**: logs an info message and skips\n\n### Linked Workflow\nThis workflow calls **Time API Logger** (ID: `6_-8RoaxFk44JBb0fvUfE`)\n\nMake sure that workflow exists and is saved before activating this one.",
